accessedAt
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

Last time the message was sent, or a request was received, for this topic.

autoDeleteOnIdle
String String

TimeSpan idle interval after which the topic is automatically deleted. The minimum duration is 5 minutes.

entityAvailabilityStatus
Nullable<EntityAvailabilityStatus> Nullable(Of EntityAvailabilityStatus)

Entity availability status for the topic. Possible values include: 'Available', 'Limited', 'Renaming', 'Restoring', 'Unknown'

createdAt
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

Exact time the message was created.

countDetails
MessageCountDetails MessageCountDetails
defaultMessageTimeToLive
String String

Default message time to live value. This is the duration after which the message expires, starting from when the message is sent to Service Bus. This is the default value used when TimeToLive is not set on a message itself.

duplicateDetectionHistoryTimeWindow
String String

TimeSpan structure that defines the duration of the duplicate detection history. The default value is 10 minutes.

enableBatchedOperations
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value that indicates whether server-side batched operations are enabled.

enableExpress
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value that indicates whether Express Entities are enabled. An express topic holds a message in memory temporarily before writing it to persistent storage.

enablePartitioning
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value that indicates whether the topic to be partitioned across multiple message brokers is enabled.

enableSubscriptionPartitioning
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value that indicates whether partitioning is enabled or disabled.

filteringMessagesBeforePublishing
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Whether messages should be filtered before publishing.

isAnonymousAccessible
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value that indicates whether the message is accessible anonymously.

isExpress
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)
maxSizeInMegabytes
Nullable<Int64> Nullable(Of Int64)

Maximum size of the topic in megabytes, which is the size of the memory allocated for the topic.

requiresDuplicateDetection
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value indicating if this topic requires duplicate detection.

sizeInBytes
Nullable<Int64> Nullable(Of Int64)

Size of the topic, in bytes.

status
Nullable<EntityStatus> Nullable(Of EntityStatus)

Enumerates the possible values for the status of a messaging entity. Possible values include: 'Active', 'Creating', 'Deleting', 'Disabled', 'ReceiveDisabled', 'Renaming', 'Restoring', 'SendDisabled', 'Unknown'

subscriptionCount
Nullable<Int32> Nullable(Of Int32)

Number of subscriptions.

supportOrdering
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value that indicates whether the topic supports ordering.

updatedAt
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

The exact time the message was updated.
